        "Id": "f27c8572-ac53-4530-ad51-aa91980ab5fe",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The tate brothers raid",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COLORADO",
        "PublicId": "109067238438",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Colorado_2/_scene_bull.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 36896e6d-cdb0-4cba-808d-74c3f564cd09).Image",
        "Description": "In the mountains of Colorado, Andrew Tate and his brother Tristan have resurfaced under fabricated identities, hiding from public view while claiming refuge from what they call the matrix. From a heavily guarded private compound, they are quietly building an illegal gambling operation designed to funnel money and influence beyond the reach of authorities. Surrounded by loyal private security and insulated by isolation, they believe themselves protected. The goal is to dismantle their operation.",
